  "title": "Enterprise Sales Account Manager (Enterprise Solutions, B2B Sales)",
  "description": "<h2>Business Development & Account Ownership</h2><ul><li><p>Manage a portfolio of enterprise customers within assigned industry verticals</p></li><li><p>Proactively identify and develop new business opportunities</p></li><li><p>Execute account strategies to expand revenue and solution adoption</p></li></ul><h2>Customer Engagement</h2><ul><li><p>Build and maintain strong working relationships with senior decision-makers and functional leaders</p></li><li><p>Understand customer priorities and align solutions to business and operational needs</p></li></ul><h2>Solution-Based Selling</h2><ul><li><p>Position enterprise solutions to address customer challenges and long-term objectives</p></li><li><p>Lead discussions around value creation, efficiency, and transformation initiatives</p></li></ul><h2>Cross-Functional Coordination</h2><ul><li><p>Partner with internal teams such as presales, marketing, and technical support to deliver end-to-end solutions</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with external partners to support implementation and delivery</p></li></ul><h2>Sales Performance Management</h2><ul><li><p>Maintain a healthy sales pipeline and provide accurate sales forecasts</p></li><li><p>Track account progress and ensure customer satisfaction</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Business, Marketing, Engineering, IT, or a related field is preferred</li><li><p>At least 5 years of experience in enterprise sales or key account management</p></li><li><p>Prior exposure to Healthcare or Manufacturing environments is advantageous</p></li><li><p>Experience selling technology, automation, AV, or enterprise solutions</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p><p><br /></p><p>Reg. No.: R23117344 (Tiong Tian Ho)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
